<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Olympias Einhander</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-18 22:19:33</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is an exceptional weapon. It cost me 750pp a good price and I am very satisfied with it. The proc can be a bit troublesome but my groups have been fine with it so far.  If need be, I carry another blade to replace it if things are not going well. </font></td></tr></table>
